##Game Mechanics


<div style= "width: 60%"> 

###A rule or an action in a game

Imagine you're playing your favorite game. What are some things you can do in the game? Maybe you can fly, run, collect coins, or jump. These actions you can perform are all examples of game mechanics. They're like the rules and tools that make the game work.

